                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="row mt-4">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="card h-100">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <h5 class="card-title">üèóÔ∏è MVC Architecture</h5>
                    <p class="card-text">
                        Built with familiar MVC pattern - Controllers, Views, Models, and Repository pattern 
