                    <ul class="mb-0 small">
                        <li><strong>Text Input</strong> - Real-time text input with validation</li>
                        <li><strong>Slider</strong> - Interactive range slider</li>
                        <li><strong>Dropdown</strong> - Selection components</li>
                        <li><strong>Buttons</strong> - Customizable action buttons</li>
                        <li><strong>Metrics</strong> - KPI displays with delta indicators</li>
                        <li><strong>Charts</strong> - Data visualization components</li>
                        <li><strong>API Integration</strong> - Repository pattern for external calls</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .card {
